    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per the MRL 2 requirements matrix. Primary validation evidence (RH benchmark across five operating points, MAE 8.3%) satisfies the pre-specified acceptance criterion. Supplementary validation of pressure rise (error 2.7%) and wall shear stress field (R = 0.91) provides additional confidence in the flow field solution. The COU1 claim that CFD can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device is supported at the Medium assurance level.",
